OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA band of rain will move south
OL,6,Fthrough the morning, clearing southern
OL,7,Fcoasts during the afternoon. A fine
OL,8,Fand settled day thereafter with plenty
OL,9,Fof sunshine. Feeling cool in brisk
OL,10,Fnortherly winds, particularly along
OL,11,Feastern coasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FClear overnight skies will
OL,14,Fallow temperatures to fall away
OL,15,Fquickly, with a rural frost developing
OL,16,Fin places. Winds falling light
OL,17,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
