OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA sunny but cold start, with
OL,6,Fcloud increasing ahead of a band of
OL,7,Finfrequent showers moving south during
OL,8,Fthe afternoon, lingering into the
OL,9,Fevening. Brisk northwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FFrequent blustery showers on Wednesday
OL,13,Fand Thursday, occasionally heavy with
OL,14,Fa risk of thunder. Friday cloudy and
OL,15,Fmostly dry, with some bright or sunny
OL,16,Fspells. Feeling rather cool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
